text-primary-foreground text-xs font-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Bricks Falling When Hit\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/bricks-falling-when-hit\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"Python\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/bricks-falling-when-hit/python\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/bricks-falling-when-hit\">Bricks Falling When Hit</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">Python</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-hard/15 text-hard\">Hard</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Bricks Falling When Hit<!-- --> — <!-- -->Python</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/bricks-falling-when-hit\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->O(r * c)<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O(r * c)</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code># Time:  O(r * c)\n# Space: O(r * c)\n\nclass UnionFind(object):\n    def __init__(self, n):\n        self.set = range(n+1)\n        self.size = [1]*(n+1)\n        self.size[-1] = 0\n\n    def find_set(self, x):\n        if self.set[x] != x:\n            self.set[x] = self.find_set(self.set[x])  # path compression.\n        return self.set[x]\n\n    def union_set(self, x, y):\n        x_root, y_root = map(self.find_set, (x, y))\n        if x_root == y_root:\n            return False\n        self.set[min(x_root, y_root)] = max(x_root, y_root)\n        self.size[max(x_root, y_root)] += self.size[min(x_root, y_root)]\n        return True\n\n    def top(self):\n        return self.size[self.find_set(len(self.size)-1)]\n\n\nclass Solution(object):\n    def hitBricks(self, grid, hits):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        :type grid: List[List[int]]\n        :type hits: List[List[int]]\n        :rtype: List[int]\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n        def index(C, r, c):\n            return r*C+c\n\n        directions = [(0, -1), (0, 1), (-1, 0), (1, 0)]\n        R, C = len(grid), len(grid[0])\n\n        hit_grid = [row[:] for row in grid]\n        for i, j in hits:\n            hit_grid[i][j] = 0\n\n        union_find = UnionFind(R*C)\n        for r, row in enumerate(hit_grid):\n            for c, val in enumerate(row):\n                if not val:\n                    continue\n                if r == 0:\n                    union_find.union_set(index(C, r, c), R*C)\n                if r and hit_grid[r-1][c]:\n                    union_find.union_set(index(C, r, c), index(C, r-1, c))\n                if c and hit_grid[r][c-1]:\n                    union_find.union_set(index(C, r, c), index(C, r, c-1))\n\n        result = []\n        for r, c in reversed(hits):\n            prev_roof = union_find.top()\n            if grid[r][c] == 0:\n                result.append(0)\n                continue\n            for d in directions:\n                nr, nc = (r+d[0], c+d[1])\n                if 0 &lt;= nr &lt; R and 0 &lt;= nc &lt; C and hit_grid[nr][nc]:\n                    union_find.union_set(index(C, r, c), index(C, nr, nc))\n            if r == 0:\n                union_find.union_set(index(C, r, c), R*C)\n            hit_grid[r][c] = 1\n            result.append(max(0, union_find.top()-prev_roof-1))\n        return result[::-1]\n\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Interview</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/interview-preparation\">Interview prep</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/system-design\">System design</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/glossary\">Glossary</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Product</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/pricing\">Pricing</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about\">About</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/about/attribution\">Attribution</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/sitemap-html\">Sitemap</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-border\"><div class=\"container-af py-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 justify-between text-xs text-muted-foreground\"><p>© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> <!-- -->AlgoForge<!-- -->. Educational use only.</p><p>Solution code sourced under MIT from<!-- -->